§ 1123. Repealed. Pub. L. 89–331, § 10, Nov. 8, 1965, 79 Stat. 1278
Section, act Aug. 8, 1947, ch. 519, title II, § 213, as added July 13, 1962, Pub. L. 87–535, § 12, 76 Stat, 163; amended July 19, 1962, Pub. L. 87–539, § 2(e), 76 Stat. 170, made provision for import fees and set the amount and basis for such fees.
Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries Effective Date of RepealRepeal effective Jan. 1, 1965, pursuant to section 14 of Pub. L. 89–331.
